Beta 3 of my Block Fort map - I'd like to thank The Bucket for his original feedback on beta 1. Beta 2 was released on the NyOm nYom server, and is basically a sexied up beta 1 with "NyOm nYom" in the sky - but if anyone would like it, please ask and I will upload.

Thank's to Logan Dougall for his Cell shader tutorial http://www.fpsbanana.com/tuts/2408 and cheers to NyOm nYom for their support and for hosting my maps. Not to mention my good CS:S mate Wild Turkey. 

There are many more maps of similar style on their way, I've been busy :)

Hope you all enjoy, any tips comments or feedback would be great.

-tankie
